divs: Sighting Detailsit was new years night i was around the campfire with my cat i looked up into the sky and there was a blinding egg like shape coming towards me then in a instant i was beamed into a very bright room with an alien face looking down at me its eyes were wide no visible nose the mouth was oval with small pointed teeth they then went over to a near by table where my cat was mutilated in front of me they then went over to me with a long tube with a softball sized ball at the end at the other end was a blinking device they then perceded to stick it up my rectum and inserted the device then everything gets fuzzy i wake with a headache and a sore rectum my cat was missing i then heared a beeping noise from inside my head then slowly over ten days began to remember this encounter the beeping has not stopped and my cat is still gone im terribly distaught please help.
